oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session - Tenille Townes and Josh Kear - 2018-06-23
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by songwriters Tenille Townes and Josh Kear from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on June 23, 2018. Includes questions from the audience.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Tenille Townes; Josh Kear;
